# Compiled binaries built from cmd/* packages.
# (Listing each by name keeps the file explicit; a bare `*` would
# accidentally exclude other things.)
/mccapture
/morningstar-sdk

# Go test artifacts.
*.test
*.out
coverage.txt
coverage.html

# Go workspace files (we don't currently use these but let's not
# commit them by accident if a contributor enables them locally).
go.work
go.work.sum

# Editor / IDE state.
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Notes:
# - pkg/mc8pro/testdata/ is INTENTIONALLY committed. The .json fixtures
#   and the .sysex binary captures in testdata/raw/ are required by the
#   unit tests in pkg/mc8pro/sysex/. They're small, reproducible via
#   `go run ./cmd/mccapture` against a live device, and let
#   `go test ./...` pass without hardware.
# - reference/ lives at the workspace root, outside this module, so
#   nothing here needs to ignore it.
